401
00:27:43,060 --> 00:27:46,120
Ten skewers, huh?

402
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:49,390
Did you think skewered grilled pork at an open-air market would be 3 baht or something?

403
00:27:49,390 --> 00:27:53,190
Geez... Since I said I'd treat you, you're trying to take advantage of me. You bastard.

404
00:27:53,190 --> 00:27:57,670
