419
00:28:43,210 --> 00:28:46,640
My stomach keeps grumbling and growling, too!

420
00:28:48,170 --> 00:28:50,110
Who said that I came late?

421
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:54,730
Never mind. Let's go and eat. I'm so hungry that my stomach keeps growling.

422
00:28:54,730 --> 00:28:55,680
Let's go.

423
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:57,030
Wait.

424
00:28:57,030 --> 00:29:02,280
What's with you now? I'm hungry! It's also really hot!

425
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:14,800
Did you wash your face today already?

426
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:19,070
