456
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,980
You don't need to give me change.

457
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:49,300
I'll pay you back, all right?

458
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:50,700
You don't need to.

459
00:30:50,700 --> 00:30:53,520
